{"tid":595981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上帝根本就唔存在","createTime":"2018-03-17T07:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T07:55:24.000Z","uid":129810,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3fc6728613d9a80f0311b7d14ef1aa9c485683","tid":595981,"uid":129810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:45:46.000Z","msg":"伊壁鳩魯悖論：<br />\n<br />\n如果是上帝想阻止&ldquo;惡&rdquo;而阻止不了，那麼上帝就是無能的；<br />\n如果是上帝能阻止&ldquo;惡&rdquo;而不願阻止，那麼上帝就是壞的；<br />\n如果是上帝既不想阻止也阻止不了&ldquo;惡&rdquo;，那麼上帝就是既無能又壞；<br />\n如果是上帝既想阻止又能阻止&ldquo;惡&rdquo;，那為什麼我們的世界充滿了&ldquo;惡&rdquo;呢？<br />\n<br />\n有無耶撚解釋下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c543fbb48c404e7dbfd3e269300e827b8290d18","tid":595981,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c75bb7319630142348f00ba0bd366f5d001670a","tid":595981,"uid":129810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c543fbb48c404e7dbfd3e269300e827b8290d18","tid":595981,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"睇來上帝真係唔存在<br />\n仲沒收你條死肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9e4c435bc962db407ab0abae5804e39e40c454","tid":595981,"uid":138264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"因為上帝給予了世人自由<br />\n所以惡的岀現是無可避免<br />\n<br />\n寬恕 赦免 悔改<br />\n給予了自由 去改變 成善"}]}